{"tid":760800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁鍾意捉海星？仲要拎返屋企煲湯！？","createTime":"2018-07-30T00:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T22:34:24.000Z","uid":79166,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"47d10a7044cf9c96a845aca6d6b181174b3594be","tid":760800,"uid":79166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:54:35.000Z","msg":"琴日去沙灘，坐咗喺附近啲位度坐，隔離坐住兩個女人，過咗冇耐有個男人拎咗10幾個海星俾佢哋，跟住佢哋好開心咁尖叫＂哇～好得意呀＂<br />\n<br />\n跟住就將啲海星翻晒肚影相，仲拎個膠袋話要拎返屋企，聽佢哋嘅對話係要拎返屋企煲湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n其中有條女人講＂將啲海星曬乾咗佢先啦， 跟住今晚拎返屋企煲湯＂<br />\n<br />\n個男人拎完海星唔夠，繼續落海搵到一隻海膽，佢哋嘗試用石頭打爛海膽，最後失敗個男人先放生隻海膽<br />\n<br />\n我當時聽到真係唔知點， 打999又冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我哋得兩個女仔，佢哋成6個40歲左右嘅男人同女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，只可以大聲講下佢哋on9、最可笑係附近啲人無人覺得有問題， 有啲人仲問佢點樣捉，所以最後都係放<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有個父母教個小朋友拎住海星影相，之後小朋友想拎返屋企，個媽咪話隻海星仲細，放生佢算啦。<br />\n但因海星離開水面，腮失去水份便難以呼吸，仲要個天咁鬼熱！<br />\n<br />\n[size=4]破壞海洋生態，可能佢哋覺得冇問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真係好可悲， 全部都係香港人</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/083906_efca4637f227b1016019c2bbf35552cd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F083906_efca4637f227b1016019c2bbf35552cd.png&h=a6ad5e88&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/083907_3556fc8fe8a48f0e9bbb62b2b0d07836.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F083907_3556fc8fe8a48f0e9bbb62b2b0d07836.png&h=8238d7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/083908_bea39eb1fcb0f06a824c0a802ed9b6b0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F083908_bea39eb1fcb0f06a824c0a802ed9b6b0.png&h=ccb4c44d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/083909_49fb056415293fba0928bba8c72705fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F083909_49fb056415293fba0928bba8c72705fd.png&h=406e25d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccc91dd00a8220c34cd10d1e24870daa724e3a53","tid":760800,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:56:05.000Z","msg":"大家都係支那畜"},{"pid":"ddc3ef010c52ce784eb3c747dcfb558beda25dec","tid":760800,"uid":47819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:56:58.000Z","msg":"港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又冇腦又貪小便宜"},{"pid":"889af913172af4aad71e2fabb15520a8f994c4de","tid":760800,"uid":79166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddc3ef010c52ce784eb3c747dcfb558beda25dec","tid":760800,"uid":47819,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T00:56:58.000Z","msg":"港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又冇腦又貪小便宜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:29:40.000Z","msg":"就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c694a650b9d82256a7bda9e455cd584a5d21acce","tid":760800,"uid":79166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f21b4c6f2fb2a3a1827e54c8638a973b6bbe72","tid":760800,"uid":72226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T18:04:50.000Z","msg":"海星應該歸觸手類<br />\n好噁心 <i